\fs36 \cf0 1. Final Architecture Plan\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 \strokec2 This project follows 
\f0\b Hexagonal Architecture (Ports and Adapters)
\f1\b0  to ensure strong separation between:\
\'95 domain logic\uc0\u8232 \'95 application use cases\u8232 \'95 infrastructure\u8232 \'95 external integrations\
The core business logic lives entirely inside the 
\f0\b domain layer
\f1\b0  and is completely independent from frameworks.\
External systems such as:\
\'95 databases\uc0\u8232 \'95 APIs\u8232 \'95 web controllers\
communicate with the domain only through 
\f0\b ports
\f1\b0 .\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa321\partightenfactor0

