Entities:\
\'95 Account\uc0\u8232 \'95 Category\u8232 \'95 Transaction\u8232 \'95 Report\u8232 \'95 User\
Characteristics:\
\'95 Implemented as Java records\uc0\u8232 \'95 Immutable\u8232 \'95 No framework annotations\u8232 \'95 No persistence concerns\u8232 \'95 No JSON annotations\
This ensures the domain remains pure and framework-independent.\
