\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 \strokec2 The domain layer contains 
\f0\b zero dependencies on frameworks
\f1\b0 .\
Spring Boot, JPA, and external libraries are confined to:\
\'95 adapters\uc0\u8232 \'95 infrastructure\
The domain communicates externally only through 
\f0\b ports
\f1\b0 .\
This keeps the business logic independent and testable.\
